---
import Button from "./ui/Button.astro";
import with_us from "../assets/img/with_us.jpg";
---

<section class="with-us-section" style={`background-image: linear-gradient(91.59deg, #FFFFFF -7.42%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 64.04%), radial-gradient(127.45% 741.98% at 28.7% 38.73%, #FFFFFF 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%), url(${with_us.src});`}>
    <p>Проведи два дня на полигоне,<br>
        и ты больше не будешь водить как прежде</p>
    <h2 class="with-us-section__title">Ты с нами?</h2>
    <div class="buttons">
        <Button href="#" style={"accent"}>Погнали</Button>
        <Button href="#">Программы и цены</Button>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .with-us-section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 550px;
        padding: var(--container-padding);
        padding-top: 90px;
        padding-bottom: 90px;
    }

    .with-us-section > p {
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 21px;
    }

    .with-us-section__title {
        font-family: 'TT Mussels';
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 80px;
        line-height: 88px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #46A5FF;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .buttons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 30px;
    }
</style>